      'Accurate is not the same as safe': 'Your disciplines distinguish truth from justice routinely: a description can be accurate and its use oppressive. Machine learning collapses the two into one score unless forced apart. This concept hands you the essay question: under what conditions does accurate classification become unsafe practice, and who decides?',
