      'Are robots racist?': 'The question is a philosophy seminar in six words: can artifacts hold moral properties, or only produce effects? This course\'s answer is pragmatic: whatever your metaphysics, the effects pattern by race and are measurable. Write about the effects; let intent remain the interesting, secondary question it is.',
